title: Disturbed DLC for Rocksmith 2014 (Reupload)
description:
This torrent is a reupload (attached the wrong .torrent file to the first one) and contains the Disturbed DLC for Rocksmith 2014.

How to install:

- Place the .psarc files in your Program Files (x86)UbisoftRocksmith 2014dlc folder
- Open the Skidrow.ini file in your Rocksmith 2014 folder (should be there when you have the DLC crack installed) and add the app IDs for these songs.


APP IDs for Disturbed DLC (Add these to your Skidrow.ini file in the Rocksmith 2014 root folder)

49=258388
50=258389
51=258390

Enjoy this DLC and support the devs by buying the game if you like it!
